---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Diffuse emission contamination in AGN lags";
import WikiLink from '../../components/WikiLink.astro';
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">Diffuse emission contamination</h1>

    <p>Diffuse emission from the broad-line region (BLR), dust, or other reprocessing regions can add variable flux that contaminates continuum inter-band delays, producing complex, non-monotonic wavelength-dependent lags that bias accretion-disk size inferences.</p>

    <h2>Links</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/steyn_2026_continuum_reverberation" text="Steyn et al. (2026)" /></li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Base>
